    "  - Official release comparison against public APIs for WordPress, TYPO3, Drupal, Joomla, etc.",
    "  - Gap classification: up to date / minor update / major update / end-of-life",
    "  - Companion extension concept — a lightweight TYPO3 extension or WordPress plugin that exposes the /version endpoint, optionally secured with a",
    "  token",
    "  - Technical notes keeping it consistent with the rest of the document's style (no Puppeteer needed for the primary path, caching, no token cost for",
